# PED::SET_PED_AO_BLOB_RENDERING

## Summary
Enable rendering of AO blobs on peds feet

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped
* **BOOL** val

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Enable/disable ped shadow (ambient occlusion). https://gfycat.com/thankfulesteemedgecko
